com.tomtom.cpp.select

Class DeltaViewUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tomtom.cpp.select.DeltaViewUtil

  • public class DeltaViewUtil
extends java.lang.Object
    DeltaViewUtil is the utility class used with DeltaView. Instead of querying Delta using three separate queries for feature, association, and attribute modifications, this class makes a single call for all three queries. The result of the method is an aggregated result of all three queries.

      • fetchAggregatedAsync

        public static <FeatureProjection,AssociationProjection,AttributeProjection> java.util.concurrent.CompletableFuture<AggregatedResult<FeatureProjection,AssociationProjection,AttributeProjection>> fetchAggregatedAsync(DeltaView view,
                                                                                                                                                                                                                       SelectQuery<FeatureProjection,FeatureEntity> featureSelect,
                                                                                                                                                                                                                       SelectQuery<AssociationProjection,AssociationEntity> associationSelect,
                                                                                                                                                                                                                       SelectQuery<AttributeProjection,FeatureAttributeEntity> attributeSelect)
        This method executes feature, association, and attribute queries against the given DeltaView, and based on the query filtering clauses, returns aggregated delta information tailored to fit the filter definition. At least one query must be provided. A missing query for an entity type results in no data returned for the given entity type.
        Type Parameters:
        FeatureProjection - projection definition for FeatureProjection's properties
        AssociationProjection - projection definition for AssociationProjection's properties
        AttributeProjection - projection definition for AttributeProjection's properties
        Parameters:
        view - reference to the DeltaView instance specifying bound view with branch and version ranges
        featureSelect - query definition for fetching FeatureProjection modification data
        associationSelect - query definition for fetching AssociationProjection modification data
        attributeSelect - query definition for fetching AttributeProjection (of FeatureProjection) modification data
        Returns:
        Returns aggregated results of individual queries.
